{"tid":1313870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方回覆指，昨日警方嘗試了解一男子，但他突然逃跑企圖跳橋 警方救回卜人","createTime":"2019-07-14T02:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T03:45:42.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"56916d24bb4df75efc3adebc073ad71a6ee5e174","tid":1313870,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:52:12.000Z","msg":"就傳媒查詢一名男子今晚（七月十三日）於警方在上水港鐵站附近進行清場期間跳出行人天橋，警方發言人回覆如下：<br />\n該男子，並以非法集體作拘捕<br />\n警方今晚在上水港鐵站清場期間，一名男子涉嫌阻礙警方防線推進，人員嘗試上前向該名男子了解，但他突然逃跑，及至上水廣場天橋時跨出欄桿，企圖躍下，人員立刻捉緊該名男子並將他救回行人天橋內。經初步調查後，該名男子涉嫌非法集結被捕。"},{"pid":"879eb84c5240b96ba26341ad3ba209d8b47b4ef3","tid":1313870,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280e38aaae72f07ad804c04bde1f8ec9252d9831","tid":1313870,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:53:41.000Z","msg":"過黎一齊研究下，我地成班都好想研究你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55044c4167e75d47a52c1470be128c294f3cce2e","tid":1313870,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:54:14.000Z","msg":"攞住警棍追住人嚟了解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來狗係咁樣了解人"},{"pid":"578eb6fccc04333b47f6ea072362584903648239","tid":1313870,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:54:53.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 想殺人咁款"},{"pid":"7f6d1d9cfa9920d2772259271ebe260b2cda0e18","tid":1313870,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T02:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c1hrx1P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc1hrx1P.jpg&h=7e0f397f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牙sir 了解唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd0e1165d5a39f9667f6